{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"7115e4d9-5cf0-4f4e-960f-bb3e13724f67","content":"Here's what you need:\n\n**Environment variables** to enable automatic dump collection on crash:\n\n| Variable | Value | Purpose |\n|---|---|---|\n| `DOTNET_DbgEnableMiniDump` | `1` | Enables automatic dump on crash |\n| `DOTNET_DbgMiniDumpType` | `4` | Full dump (1=Normal, 2=WithHeap, 3=Triage, 4=Full) |\n| `DOTNET_DbgMiniDumpName` | `/tmp/dumps/coredump.%p.%t` | Dump path (`%p`=PID, `%t`=timestamp) |\n| `DOTNET_DbgCreatedumpPath` | `/opt/tools/createdump` | Non-default createdump location |\n| `DOTNET_CreateDumpDiagnostics` | `1` | *(Optional)* Logs createdump activity to stderr |\n\n**Pod spec patch:**\n\n```yaml\nspec:\n  containers:\n    - name: your-app\n      env:\n        - name: DOTNET_DbgEnableMiniDump\n          value: \"1\"\n        - name: DOTNET_DbgMiniDumpType\n          value: \"4\"\n        - name: DOTNET_DbgMiniDumpName\n          value: \"/tmp/dumps/coredump.%p.%t\"\n        - name: DOTNET_DbgCreatedumpPath\n          value: \"/opt/tools/createdump\"\n        - name: DOTNET_CreateDumpDiagnostics\n          value: \"1\"\n      volumeMounts:\n        - name: dump-volume\n          mountPath: /tmp/dumps\n  volumes:\n    - name: dump-volume\n      emptyDir:\n        sizeLimit: 4Gi   # adjust to your app's memory footprint\n```\n\n**Key notes:**\n\n- **`sizeLimit`** — set this to at least your container's memory limit since type `4` (Full) dumps the entire process memory.\n- **`ptrace` capability** — `createdump` needs `SYS_PTRACE`. If your pod runs with a restricted `securityContext`, add:\n  ```yaml\n  securityContext:\n    capabilities:\n      add: [\"SYS_PTRACE\"]\n  ```\n- **Retrieving dumps** — since `emptyDir` is ephemeral, copy dumps out before the pod is deleted (`kubectl cp`) or swap the volume for a `PersistentVolumeClaim`.\n- Lower `DbgMiniDumpType` to `2` (WithHeap) if full dumps are too large.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"41a57e1c-8e8b-463c-beb9-3af528bf5ca5","outputTokens":638,"requestId":"CB14:3DEB8E:1DEB2BC:21313A1:6A05298D"},"id":"135d2e20-1f3d-444b-9b8d-2a9f2448c11a","timestamp":"2026-05-14T01:47:05.037Z","parentId":"cdb7aaab-d737-47c6-8de5-99c2a348d42b"}
